create function volumen_auslesen (@Ebene1 smallint,@Ebene2 smallint,@Ebene3 smallint,@Ebene4 smallint, @idnr integer, @zeitraum datetime) RETURNS int AS begin declare @volumen1 int select @volumen1=sum (volumen) from VOL_MONATSVOLUMEN where Ebene1=@Ebene1 and Ebene2=@Ebene2 and Ebene3=@Ebene3 and Ebene4=@Ebene4 and IDNR=@IDNR and der_erste_monat_jahr=@zeitraum return @volumen1 end
